          <h3>SENAVIA Corp is headquartered in Plantation. Broward is home — and it's where our retainer client base is strongest.</h3>
          <p>From Fort Lauderdale's coastal commerce to Pembroke Pines' suburban service economy, Broward businesses operate in a tight, networked market. We help local contractors, retailers, and professional firms own their corner of it — through clean web architecture, conversion-tuned landing pages, and a Google Business Profile strategy that gets calls.</p>
